#: ../../O/OT.rst:9
msgid ""
"[Usenet: common] Abbreviation for \"off-topic\". This is used to respond to "
"a question that is inappropriate for the newsgroup that the questioner "
"posted to. Often used in an HTML-style modifier or with adverbs. See also "
":ref:`TAN`\\."
msgstr ""
"[Usenet: 一般的] \"off-"
"topic\"の略語。質問者が投稿したニュースグループにふさわしくない質問に応えるのに使われる。しばしばHTML風の修飾子の中で、または副詞とともに使われる。\\"
" :ref:`TAN`\\ も参照。"
